274
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:21,080
<i>I ran from her.</i>

275
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:25,000
<i>I didn't help her.</i>

276
00:29:29,040 --> 00:29:31,320
<i>I'm the reason she became this.</i>

277
00:29:37,840 --> 00:29:42,680
