297
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:39,760
Even if you didn't ask me that,
I'd do it anyway.

298
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:47,080
<i>It's evidently clear</i>
<i>that she's also a victim.</i>

299
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,040
YOU HAVE NEW MESSAGE!!

300
00:31:52,120 --> 00:31:53,440
<i>Those people's victim.</i>

301
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:59,440
<i>If we don't hurry up and do something...</i>

302
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:03,840
she's definitely going to die soon.

303
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:06,360
What do you mean?

304
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:15,640
Since you're willing
to tell me your story...

305
00:32:17,560 --> 00:32:19,560
I'll tell you about mine.

306
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:22,440
SAVED BY A MIRACLE! MAN SURVIVES CAR CRASH
BECAUSE OF PROTECTIVE SPELL

307
00:32:22,520 --> 00:32:26,600
<i>I told you before</i>
<i>that most occult stuff you see,</i>

308
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:29,520
<i>especially on the Internet,</i>
<i>are most likely fake.</i>

309
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:31,680
<i>But much deeper into it all,</i>

310
00:32:33,120 --> 00:32:34,880
the occult exists.

311
00:32:35,800 --> 00:32:37,880
It diverges into two main disciplines.

312
00:32:40,560 --> 00:32:41,600
First,

313
00:32:43,680 --> 00:32:44,840
the White Arts,

314
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:46,920
also called the <i>Dharma-khun.</i>

315
00:32:47,800 --> 00:32:50,960
<i>Practitioners in this discipline</i>
<i>focus on Vipassana meditation.</i>

316
00:32:51,040 --> 00:32:53,960
<i>Any magic resulting from this practice</i>

317
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:57,040
is mostly used for good, to help people.

318
00:32:58,760 --> 00:33:00,280
The other discipline

319
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:03,200
is the Black Arts.

320
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:07,800
<i>This focuses on black magic and spirits.</i>

321
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:11,280
<i>These practitioners use their knowledge</i>
<i>in a negative way,</i>

322
00:33:11,360 --> 00:33:15,800
<i>abuse it for bad things,</i>
<i>for their own gains, or to hurt people.</i>

323
00:33:15,880 --> 00:33:21,600
Both arts exist, but that doesn't mean
any lay person can easily learn them.

324
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:25,640
Its conditions are far too complex
and too difficult to meet.

325
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:31,720
Normally these people keep to themselves.
They don't flaunt around who they are.

326
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:35,320
But there is one group

327
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:41,920
who believes the occult
should be tangible and verifiable.

328
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:43,760
CHANGE YOUR FATE!
POPULARITY SPELL - GURU PANYA

329
00:33:43,840 --> 00:33:48,480
<i>That makes them understand</i>
<i>the occult more than anyone.</i>

330
00:33:53,040 --> 00:33:55,880
<i>They hide in the deepest part of society.</i>

331
00:33:56,680 --> 00:33:58,800
These people are called...

332
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:01,320
Enigma.

333
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:04,800
<i>Nobody knows who Enigma is.</i>

334
00:34:05,800 --> 00:34:08,840
But we know they're
more adept in the occult than anyone.

335
00:34:10,040 --> 00:34:12,320
<i>Better than anyone in the world.</i>

336
00:34:13,720 --> 00:34:19,760
Enigma is looking for people in despair
to do business with them.

337
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:23,560
They probably reached out to Namsai

338
00:34:24,200 --> 00:34:27,520
<i>and all she has to do is</i>
<i>move according to their orders.</i>

339
00:34:32,720 --> 00:34:33,760
What about you?

340
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:38,880
Sorry. I can't say much right now.

341
00:34:39,560 --> 00:34:43,520
What I can tell you is
that I am hunting down Enigma.

342
00:34:48,200 --> 00:34:50,360
<i>I've always been hunting them down.</i>

343
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:58,480
<i>I got intel</i>
<i>that they might be in this school.</i>

344
00:34:59,680 --> 00:35:02,560
<i>That's why I came here undercover,</i>
<i>as you know.</i>

345
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:07,520
Then again, I thought I might have
misunderstood this whole mess.

346
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:09,960
But as it turned out,

347
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:13,160
Enigma really is borrowing Namsai's hands.

348
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,680
I don't get it.

349
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,720
Why would Enigma do all this?

350
00:35:22,560 --> 00:35:24,520
What do they get
from making Namsai do all this?

351
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:28,080
Firstly, it's probably for money.

352
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:42,440
<i>Businesses that claim to change</i>
<i>people's luck always prosper.</i>

353
00:35:43,640 --> 00:35:48,120
The next thing they want
is probably to see the world burn.

354
00:35:48,200 --> 00:35:50,520
Because the more messy the world is,

355
00:35:50,600 --> 00:35:53,160
the more people
turn to their superstitions.

356
00:35:54,680 --> 00:35:58,880
But no one knows for sure
what their end goal is.

357
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:04,360
What I know is
that they're abusing their victims.

358
00:36:05,040 --> 00:36:08,600
These dangerous things
come at a cost for the user.

359
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:12,360
From what I estimated of Namsai,

360
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:14,840
if we don't do anything now,

361
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:17,600
within two days,

362
00:36:18,200 --> 00:36:19,600
