363
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:24,280
Can we really save Namsai?
Do you have a plan?

364
00:36:24,760 --> 00:36:27,400
What do you need me to do?
I'll do anything.

365
00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:29,000
- Please.
- I heard you already.

366
00:36:29,720 --> 00:36:31,720
But before you worry about your friend,

367
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,680
