370
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:06,880
Don't worry.

371
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:10,480
I'll save Namsai.

372
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:15,040
I won't ever let anyone else die.

373
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,520
You ready?

374
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:23,640
Good. Let's get going.

375
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,800
<i>Like I said.</i>

376
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:37,680
<i>Namsai has no more than two days left.</i>

377
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:43,680
<i>That means today is our last chance.</i>

378
00:39:15,200 --> 00:39:18,080
