393
00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:19,120
How long...

394
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:22,040
have you been taking this medicine?

395
00:40:22,120 --> 00:40:23,680
Don't worry about me.

396
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:28,040
I work in the industry
so I know how to take good care of myself.

397
00:40:29,600 --> 00:40:33,720
